## Summary of changes (VIS003)

**Files modified:**
- `src/components/list/list.scss` — Added `scroll-behavior: smooth`, `scroll-snap-type: y proximity`, `-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch` to `.list`. Added `prefers-reduced-motion` media query to disable smooth scroll and snap.
- `src/components/list/list_item/list_item.scss` — Added `scroll-snap-align: start` to `.list-item`.
- `src/components/list/list.tsx` — Updated `scrollIntoView` to use `behavior: 'smooth'` for keyboard navigation.

**Key design decisions:**
- `scroll-snap-type: y proximity` (not `mandatory`) — only snaps when close to a boundary, doesn't interfere with free scrolling or fast keyboard navigation
- `-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch` — native momentum on iOS/Safari
- `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` disables both smooth scroll and snap — accessibility-first

